data.text:
Ambassador of the Kingdom of Thailand to Lao PDR, paid a courtesy call on H.E. Mr. Thongsavanh Phomvihane, Chairman of the Committee for External Relations of the Central Committee of the Lao People’s Revolutionary Party on the occasion of her assumption of duty

On 7 March 2023, Ms. Morakot Sriswasdi, Ambassador of the Kingdom of Thailand to Lao PDR, paid a courtesy call on H.E. Mr. Thongsavanh Phomvihane, Chairman of the Committee for External Relations of the Central Committee of the Lao People’s Revolutionary Party on the occasion of her assumption of duty. Both sides agreed to work closely to further promote bilateral relations and cooperation in all dimensions, especially people-to-people cooperation.
